    "created_at": "2014-05-29T16:59:16Z",
    "updated_at": "2014-05-29T16:59:16Z",
    "body": "We may want to reconsider DynamicLibrary's Drop impl. It caused some very confusing segfaults when I was working on the external syntax extension stuff when @Trait destructors ran during cycle annihilation way after the libraries were unloaded. I think adding an opt-in by value close method (maybe even unsafe?) would be a better idea.\n",
